<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1951-08-07T10:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1951-08-07T10:00:00-05:00" n="343" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d343">
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#center">No. 343</seg>
                            </opener>
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">740.5/8–751: Telegram</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Norway (<persName corresp="#p_BCU1" type="from">Bay</persName>) to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                                </hi><note n="1" xml:id="d343fn1">Repeated to London for <persName corresp="#p_SCM1">Spofford</persName> and to Paris for
                                        <persName corresp="#p_MAGD1">MacArthur</persName>.</note>
                            </head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#left">
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">top secret</hi>
                                </seg>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Oslo</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1951-08-07T16:00:00+01:00">August
                                        7, 1951—4 p.m.</date>
                                </dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>143. I discussed with <gloss target="#t_FonMin1">FonMin</gloss> today
                                visit to Nor of technical reps <gloss target="#t_Def1">Def</gloss>
                                and State as requested <gloss target="#t_Deptel1">Deptel</gloss> 104
                                Aug 1<note n="2" xml:id="d343fn2">
                                    <hi rend="italic">Supra</hi>.</note> rptd London <gloss target="#t_Todep1">Todep</gloss> 66 and Paris as <gloss target="#t_intel1">intel</gloss> Aug 2, 8 a.m. <gloss target="#t_FonMin1">FonMin</gloss> stated that govt prepared
                                receive team but that he will have to discuss time with <gloss target="#t_DefMin1">DefMin</gloss>. Most Mins now returning from
                                vacation, with <gloss target="#t_PriMin1">PriMin</gloss> scheduled
                                return Aug 19. He will let us know Nor Govt preference as to time
                                but indicated possibly week of Aug 20.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <persName corresp="#p_BCU1">
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bay</hi>
                                    </persName>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>